Summary: An inetd-based Linux FTP daemon.
Name: bftpd
Version: VERSION
Release: 1
Copyright: GPL
Group: System Environment/Daemons
Source: http://c.codercity.de/bruksoft/bftpd/bftpd-VERSION.tar.gz

%description
bftpd is a Linux FTP server with chroot and setreuid. Not all FTP commands are
included. It doesn't need special home directory preparation and accesses
either the user's home directory or its .ftp subdirectory, and user
authentication is via passwd/shadow or PAM.

%files
%defattr (-, root, root)
/etc/bftpd.conf
/usr/sbin/bftpd

